        "subject": "LU-1333 hsm: Add hsm_release feature.",
        "message": "LU-1333 hsm: Add hsm_release feature.\n\nHSM Release is one of the key feature of HSM. It removes file\nLOV objects, if the file has been archived previously.\n\nThis patch is implementing all mechanisms, from client to MDS,\nto do a release, modifying LOV EA, triggering actions and checking\nthe file is in a correct state.\n\nSigned-off-by: Aurelien Degremont <aurelien.degremont@cea.fr>\nChange-Id: I6eb13a80c05c6c81ce36ec6c90d5a0ad67f3e907\n"
